query: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/routeStart> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Piccadilly> }

text: What is the name of the university where Obama's wife studied?
query: SELECT DISTINCT ?s WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barack_Obama> <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/spouse> ?x . ?x <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/almaMater> ?s }

text: When did Paraguay proclaim its independence?
query: SELECT DISTINCT ?date WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paraguay> <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/foundingDate> ?date }

text: How short is the shortest active NBA player?
query: SELECT DISTINCT ?n WHERE { ?x a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/BasketballPlayer> ; <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/league> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association> ; <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/height> ?n FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?x <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/activeYearsEndYear> ?d } } ORDER BY ASC(?n) OFFSET 0 LIMIT 1

text: Where did Abraham Lincoln die?
query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { res:Abraham_Lincoln dbo:deathPlace ?uri }

text: When was Jack Wolfskin founded?
query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT xsd:date(?year) WHERE { res:Jack_Wolfskin dbo:foundingYear ?year }

text: What is the founding year of the brewery that produces Pilsner Urquell?
query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> SELECT DISTINCT xsd:date(?num) WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pilsner_Urquell> <http://dbpedia.org/property/brewery> ?uri . ?uri dbo:foundingYear ?num }

text: When did the Boston Tea Party take place?
query: SELECT DISTINCT ?d WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_Tea_Party> <http://dbpedia.org/property/date> ?d }

text: Which animals are critically endangered?
query: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Animal> ; <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/conservationStatus> "CR" }

text: Which politicians were married to a German?
query: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Politician> ; <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/spouse> ?spouse { ?spouse <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/birthPlace> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany> } UNION { ?spouse <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/birthPlace> ?p . ?p <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/country> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany> } }

text: How big is the earth's diameter?
query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT (( xsd:double(?radius) * 2 ) AS ?diameter) WHERE { res:Earth dbo:meanRadius ?radius }

text: Is the wife of President Obama called Michelle?
query: PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX onto: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> ASK WHERE { res:Barack_Obama onto:spouse ?spouse . ?spouse rdfs:label ?name FILTER regex(?name, "Michelle") }

text: When did Muhammad die?
query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT xsd:date(?date) WHERE { res:Muhammad dbo:deathDate ?date }

text: What is the atmosphere of the Moon composed of?
query: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moon> <http://dbpedia.org/property/atmosphereComposition> ?uri }

text: Who is the governor of Texas?
query: PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> SELECT DISTINCT ?string WHERE { res:Texas dbp:governor ?string }

text: Which movies did Kurosawa direct?
query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Film ; dbo:director res:Akira_Kurosawa }

text: What was the name of the famous battle in 1836 in San Antonio?
query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT ?uri WHERE { ?uri a dbo:MilitaryConflict ; dbo:place dbr:San_Antonio ; dbo:date ?date FILTER ( ?date > "1835-12-31T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime ) FILTER ( ?date <= "1836-12-31T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime ) }

text: Give me the official websites of actors of the television show Charmed.
query: PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX foaf: <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/> PREFIX onto: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charmed> onto:starring ?actors . ?actors foaf:homepage ?uri }

text: How many calories does a baguette have?
query: SELECT DISTINCT ?n WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Baguette> <http://dbpedia.org/property/calories> ?n }

text: Give me all libraries established before 1400.
query: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Library> ; <http://dbpedia.org/property/established> ?year FILTER ( ?year < 1400 ) }

text: Which museum exhibits The Scream by Munch?
query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { res:The_Scream dbo:museum ?uri }

text: When was the De Beers company founded?
query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT xsd:date(?date) WHERE { res:De_Beers dbo:foundingYear ?date }

text: Who became president after JFK died?
query: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_F._Kennedy> <http://dbpedia.org/property/presidentEnd> ?x . ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/property/presidentStart> ?x; a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Person>. }

text: Who are the parents of the wife of Juan Carlos I?
query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { res:Juan_Carlos_I_of_Spain dbo:spouse ?x . ?x dbo:parent ?uri }

text: Who is the novelist of the work a song of ice and fire?
query: PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> SELECT ?Novelist WHERE { dbr:A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire dbp:author ?Novelist }

text: In which studio did the Beatles record their first album?
query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX db: <http://dbpedia.org/> SELECT ?studio WHERE { ?album dbo:artist dbr:The_Beatles ; rdf:type dbo:Album ; dbo:releaseDate ?date ; dbp:studio ?studio } ORDER BY ASC(?date) LIMIT 1

text: When did princess Diana die?
query: SELECT DISTINCT xsd:date(?d) WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diana,_Princess_of_Wales> <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/deathDate> ?d }

text: Who founded Intel?
query: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Intel> <http://dbpedia.org/property/founders> ?uri }

text: Who is the youngest player in the Premier League?
query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri dbo:team ?team . ?league dbo:league res:Premier_League . ?league dbo:team ?team . ?uri dbo:birthDate ?date } ORDER BY DESC(?date) LIMIT 1

text: Which instruments does Cat Stevens play?
query: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens> <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/instrument> ?uri }

text: Which bridges are of the same type as the Manhattan Bridge?
query: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?bridge WHERE { dbr:Manhattan_Bridge dbo:type ?type . ?bridge dbo:type ?type ; rdf:type dbo:Bridge }

text: How many companies were founded by the founder of Facebook?
query: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?x) AS ?c) WHERE { <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Facebook> <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/foundedBy> ?uri . ?x <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/foundedBy> ?uri }

text: Show me hiking trails in the Grand Canyon where there's no danger of flash floods.
query: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/property/trailheads> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Canyon> FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/property/hazards> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flash_flood> } }
